				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/C%C3%B4-nh%E1%BA%A1n-H%E1%BA%ADu-phi-nh%E1%BA%A1n/poem-3hhBDlSkWeBPfZtXuxM8uQ">Cô nhạn - Hậu phi nhạn - 孤雁－後飛雁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/Dao-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Vi%C3%AAn-Ngo%E1%BA%A1i-Th%E1%BA%A9m-Ng%C3%B4n-qu%C3%A1-l%C4%A9nh/poem-8apGbg3g29a526OGGh0qCw">Dao đồng Đỗ Viên Ngoại Thẩm Ngôn quá lĩnh - 遙同杜員外審言過嶺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/author-eVhiQaGgvOZuXB8qH633Iw">Thẩm Thuyên Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chung-Tinh/%C4%90%C3%A0o-hoa-gi%E1%BA%A3n-c%E1%BB%95-%C4%91%E1%BA%B1ng-ca/poem-hS_TP5P43oizwkfGhNGt9Q">Đào hoa giản cổ đằng ca - 桃花澗古藤歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chung-Tinh/author-u6-RIhUvEY9JL42vswhrag">Chung Tinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-K%E1%BA%BF/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Th%C3%A1i-Nguy%C3%AAn-th%E1%BA%A5t-nh%E1%BA%ADt-quang-ph%E1%BB%A5c-k%C3%BD-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-dnsqk3ZOV2TRMVHxlSyGhg">Đề Thái Nguyên thất nhật quang phục ký kỳ 4 - 題太七日光復記其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-K%E1%BA%BF/author-SslMhW8LozZDjTCazfC2iQ">Ngô Đức Kế</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/L%E1%BA%A1c-Trung-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-Vi%C3%AAn-th%E1%BA%ADp-di-b%E1%BA%A5t-ng%E1%BB%99/poem-5Hb_gTG1uyvs0hq5_xSWzg">Lạc Trung phỏng Viên thập di bất ngộ - 洛中訪袁拾遺不遇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/author-ep8IiRc7UH2qX75S-LVnLw">Mạnh Hạo Nhiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-K%E1%BB%B7/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-c%C3%B4ng/poem-pYnPVxgeaRGvI-U4EiVnqw">Nguyễn tướng công - 阮相公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-K%E1%BB%B7/author-W0I69OcXMQDwUq9bWbb_pQ">Bùi Kỷ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/Nh%E1%BA%A1n-M%C3%B4n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung-th%C6%B0-s%E1%BB%9F-ki%E1%BA%BFn/poem-ADWMl8DYhFQsSXDLb3Yo_g">Nhạn Môn đạo trung thư sở kiến - 雁門道中書所見</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-lCIs61Hzjl6rqKSiwGq6ow">Nguyên Hiếu Vấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-nh%E1%BB%8B-vi%C3%AAn-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-M%E1%BA%A1c-Ng%C3%B4-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-U%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BA%B7c-u%E1%BB%95ng-gi%C3%A1-khuy%E1%BA%BFt-tri%E1%BB%83n-%C4%91%C3%A3i-li%C3%AAu-k%C3%BD-th%E1%BB%AD-t%C3%A1c/poem-xyVX9vKnkXj8cUvqXzLICw">Phạm nhị viên ngoại Mạc, Ngô thập thị ngự Uất đặc uổng giá khuyết triển đãi, liêu ký thử tác - 范二員外邈、吳十侍禦鬱特枉駕闕展待，聊寄此作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A3o-ph%C3%A1t/poem-QTVFJ9Z0-BPrKIIARvfJrA">Tảo phát - 早發</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/T%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-59bbiMoAqO5NHisLww9MMw">Tức cảnh kỳ 1 - 即景其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
